title: Helping Others Improve EP 23#

embed.description: Don't buy quick Silver sash as AP, get Banshies instead. -- Twitter: https://twitter.com/YaseiDoubutsu Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/YaseiDoubutsuXD/ Pateron: https://t.co/pQ5xovdbqe -- This is part of a series, where I try and help others go from Bronze to silver. Heck maybe even gold. I'm not the one playing, I'm spectating a game.

body:
I get a little mad at this long game.
Pick out anything I may have missed, and all that jazz.
